	<element name="Teleportation" type="Archetype" source="JJK" id="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_TELEPORTATION">
		<supports>Innate Technique</supports>
		<description>
			<p>You can teleport yourself and others to marked locations while not being viewed.</p>
			<div element="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_TELEPORT" />
			<div element="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_IMPROVED_TELEPORT" />
			<div element="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_MASTERED_TELEPORT" />
			<div element="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_IMPROVED_MARKING" />
			<div element="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_DOMAIN_EXPANSION_CROSSROADS_OF_INSTANCE" />
		</description>
		<sheet display="false">
			<description>You can teleport yourself and others to marked locations while not being viewed.</description>
		</sheet>
		<rules>
			<grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_TELEPORT" level="1" />
			<grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_IMPROVED_TELEPORT" level="3" />
			<grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_MASTERED_TELEPORT" level="6" />
			<grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_IMPROVED_MARKING" level="11" />
			<grant type="Archetype Feature" id="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_DOMAIN_EXPANSION_CROSSROADS_OF_INSTANCE" level="18" />
		</rules>
	</element>

	<element name="Teleport" type="Archetype Feature" source="JJK" id="ID_JJK_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_TELEPORTATION_TELEPORT">
		<requirements>!ID_INTERNAL_FEATURE_REPLACEMENT_TELEPORTATION_TELEPORT</requirements>
		<description>
			<p>Beginning at 1st level, your technique allows you to teleport to destinations you have marked. As a bonus action for 1 cursed energy, you can mark a person, location, or object which you can touch. You can have up to twice your CE modifier in marks at once and your marks remain for up to 12 hours. You can remove any of your marks at will.</p>
            <p class="indent">As an action for 2 cursed energy, while not being viewed, you and any willing creatures within 5ft of you that are also not being viewed teleport up to 500 feet to a mark of your choice.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet action="Bonus Action" usage="CE">
			<description>For 1 CE, you can mark a person, location, or object which you can touch. You can have up to {{teleportation:marks:max}} marks at once and your marks remain for up to 12 hours. You can remove any of your marks at will. As an action for 2 CE, while not being viewed, you and any willing creatures within 5ft of you that are also not being viewed teleport up to {{teleportation:range}} feet to a mark of your choice.</description>
            <description level="3">For 1 CE, you can mark a person, location, or object which you can touch. You can have up to {{teleportation:marks:max}} marks at once and your marks remain for up to 12 hours. You can remove any of your marks at will. As an action or reaction to an attack or saving throw as long as you have a way to cause yourself to disappear from view for 2 CE, while not being viewed, you and any willing creatures within 5ft of you that are also not being viewed teleport up to {{teleportation:range}} feet to a mark of your choice.</description>
            <description level="6">For 1 CE, you can mark a person, location, or object which you can touch. You can have up to {{teleportation:marks:max}} marks at once and your marks remain for up a week. You can remove any of your marks at will. As an action or reaction to an attack or saving throw as long as you have a way to cause yourself to disappear from view for 2 CE, while not being viewed, you and any willing creatures within 5ft of you that are also not being viewed teleport up to {{teleportation:range}} feet to a mark of your choice.</description>
            <description level="6" action="Free Action">For 1 CE, you can mark a person, location, or object which you can touch. You can have up to {{teleportation:marks:max}} marks at once and your marks remain for up a week. You can remove any of your marks at will. As an action or reaction to an attack or saving throw as long as you have a way to cause yourself to disappear from view for 2 CE, while not being viewed, you and any willing creatures within 5ft of you that are also not being viewed teleport up to {{teleportation:range}} feet to a mark of your choice.</description>
		</sheet>
